{
  "stem": "13313.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, whatever he-- he used to, to feast those people, to honor them, to celebrate them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they also did some business with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He managed to get some, some, some highly desirable goods like, like, alcohol, cigarettes, and chocolates, and used to get them as gifts or at a cheap price.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to go with my dad with heavy suitcases to the, to the countryside, to the inns, inns and cafes and parks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had that little black market going in contraband and, and smuggling this, this stuff through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so, as a matter of fact, the experience we-- we were living, as I said, in orange crates.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had practically no money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every Friday night, my mother used to give us five francs, my brother and I, to go to the swimming club, which was about 10 minutes walk from home.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Astrid Batt it was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Astrid Swimming Club in the [NON-ENGLISH] to go and swim and take a shower to be cleansed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That one particular Friday, that, that week that opened up in the Rex Theater on the main street of Antwerp on the De Keyserlei, the movie, which was a 1939 beginning of the war movie, or middle of the war movie.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the Europeans to have after all this Nazi propaganda was something unreal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was dying to go and see that movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was also five francs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my mother, Mama, please could we go to the movie?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was dying to see this movie, All the kids are talking about She says no, I only have five francs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Be a good boy and go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't go to the movie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Take your brother and go to the swimming club.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
